### MongoDB Localization Field Path Migration for Nested Localized Fields

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/migration-guide/overview.mdx

Payload now automatically removes redundant localized properties from sub-fields when a parent is localized. This example shows how MongoDB field paths for localized nested fields should be updated to reflect the simplified structure, removing unnecessary locale indicators.

```diff
- layout.columns.en.link.en.type.en
+ layout.columns.en.link.type
```

